    "/v1/images/edits": {
      "post": {
        "operationId": "post_gpt_image_2___",
        "summary": "gpt-image-2图生图",
        "tags": [
          "OpenAI 格式"
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "请求成功"
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "未授权"
          },
          "429": {
            "description": "超出速率限制"
          }
        },
        "description": "model：模型名称   gpt-image-2 官方名称，gpt-image-2 逆向\nprompt：提示词输入\n\nsize 的参数为：\nPopular sizes 常用尺码\n1024x1024 (square)\n\n1536x1024 (landscape)\n\n1024x1536 (portrait)\n\n2048x2048 (2K square)\n\n2048x1152 (2K landscape)\n\n3840x2160 (4K landscape)\n\n2160x3840 (4K portrait)\nauto (default)\n\nquality：质量\nlow\nmedium\nhigh\nauto\n\ninput_fidelity：\nlow\nmedium\nhigh\nauto\n\nresponse_format:出参格式 url 和 base64，当前只支持 base64 出参\nimage：传入图片，base64 和 url 均可",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object"
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
